-defined networking architecture. Lastly, numerical\nresults validate the convergence of the proposed algorithm and the significant\nimprovement on network utility, load balancing and user fairness.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Apr 2015 11:50:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 8 Mar 2016 11:30:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-09"}
