r of interatomic magnetic interactions, main\ncontributions to the magnetocrystalline anisotropy and the spin canting, as\nwell as the similarities and differences of the proposed picture from the\nphenomenological model of spin-dependent p-d hybridization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Apr 2015 13:41:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
